{
  "page": "Feature quote/274",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“I will be <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">married</a>. Why shouldn't I be? You were married at my age. I shall be wedded and bedded, but to whom? <a href=\"/index.php/Jonah_Mooton\" title=\"Jonah Mooton\">Jonah</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Roy_Connington\" title=\"Roy Connington\">Roy</a> both love me, I could take one of them, but they are both such boys. <a href=\"/index.php/Braxton_Beesbury\" title=\"Braxton Beesbury\">Stinger</a> does not love me, but he makes me laugh and sometimes makes me scream. I could marry all three of them, why not? Why should I have just one husband? <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">The Conqueror</a> had two wives, and <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor</a> had six or eight.” —Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Saera_Targaryen\" title=\"Saera Targaryen\">Saera Targaryen</a><br />“You would compare yourself to <i>Maegor</i>? Is that who you aspire to be?” —King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.0A.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign 